Zephyr RTOS:
	Zephyr RTOS is the open source and that supports the different architectures.
	Mainly used for IoT based solution.
	It is written in C language and provided license under Apache open source License.
	It is Secure and looks like powerful RTOS for the embedded appplications.
	It supports different communications like Bluetooth,CAN,IP ,etc. Looks good for the  working with Zephyr RTOS and the working with different architectures and boards.
